comment: CGV Vincom Xuan Khanh is the ideal place to enjoy blockbuster movies in a modern and comfortable space. Located in Vincom Xuan Khanh shopping center, the theater is easy to find and convenient for combining movie watching, shopping and dining.  The theater has many spacious, clean screening rooms, equipped with a vivid Dolby sound system, a large, sharp screen and soft seats, creating a comfortable feeling even if you sit and watch a movie for several hours. In particular, the seats are arranged scientifically, making every viewing angle clear without being obscured.  The popcorn counter is rich with diverse combos, crispy and fragrant popcorn. The service staff is quick, cheerful and provides dedicated customer support. The theater also regularly has attractive promotions such as ticket discounts for students or incentives when booking tickets online.  With good service quality, CGV Vincom Xuan Khanh deserves to be a familiar destination for movie enthusiasts in Can Tho. Come and experience now!

comment: If I had a 0-star rating, I would send it to the theater for my bad experience yesterday! - Specifically, at 9:24 PM on November 27, 2024 (with information on the ticket), me and my friend (2 people) entered the theater to buy tickets at the counter, we bought 2 Linh Mieu tickets for the 9:30 show. PM and include 1 corn and 1 drink (I told the Staff the same thing); At first, you also asked us if eating corn tasted like anything. I also told you that I ate regular corn (EMPLOYED THAT FROM THE FIRST I SAID REGULAR CORN), then I looked at the order screen and it showed 1. What kind of COMBO (COMBO with a picture of this and that costs 200 or so) and she said 1 corn of cheese? I told my friend that I would only take 1 regular coke and 1 regular corn. At this time, when he received the order, he continued to press another COMBO (140 or 160, I don't remember), so I asked again. The friend asked again: "Sister, how much is 1 corn and 1 drink?", she answered me "122k", then she clicked on the screen which combo is 109k with 1 snack package as shown in the picture (while just now you answered me it was 122k? üòá), at this point I was also very upset and didn't want to talk anymore so I accepted the payment and went to the theater to watch the movie because it was almost there. now. At first, I just thought it was because of work that you had to be like that, so from the beginning, when I wasn't asked by the staff first and automatically pressed the combo in a drink cup of this or that shape, I didn't say anything and asked my friend. give me 1 regular popcorn but 5 times 7 times you force me into another combo and even deliberately give me cheese popcorn when from the beginning I said to use regular flavor? - I know that the company also has requirements and you are all carefully trained to push these Extra Combos, but this will be something that makes customers very unhappy, because they feel they are not respected. , deceiving customers and also a contemptuous attitude toward customers. I also work in the F&B industry and I also know what it's like to run a service. If the company wants to promote sales, instead of intentionally forcing customers like that, they should use another strategy to call customers, not force them to work. Employees must run KPIs every day like that. - My experience yesterday was very unsatisfactory. I hope the theater will contact us to resolve it and receive a satisfactory apology. I love going to the movies but have never felt so uncomfortable!!!
